data.title: Find a Program
data.meta_description: Connecticut State Community College promotes student success through affordable access to academically rigorous and innovate education, career training, and lifelong learning.
data.text:
Key:

On-Ground: All courses within the program may be taken in person at a CT State campus or training center

Hybrid: Some courses within the program may be taken online while others are only available on-ground

Online: All courses within the program may be completed online
